3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Musk%20is%20not%20one%20to%20shy%20away%20from%20the%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20something%20is%20important%20enough%2C%20you%20do%20it%2C%20even%20if%20the%20odds%20are%20not%20in%20your%20favor%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20told%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%26quot%3B%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20with%20whom%20Musk%20is%20currently%20engaged%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhistory-of-elon-musk-and-sam-altman-relationship-feuds-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegal%20battle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20put%20it%20another%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElon%20desperately%20wants%20the%20world%20to%20be%20saved.%20But%20only%20if%20he%20can%20be%20the%20one%20to%20save%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said%20in%20a%202023%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20challenges%20arise%20at%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-doge-spacex-leadership-limits-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMusk's%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20%26quot%3Bgoes%20all%20in%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Andy%20Wu%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20business%20administration%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School%2C%20previously%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20founded%20SpaceX%20a%20decade%20earlier%2C%20easily%20his%20most%20ambitious%20project%2C%20investing%20%24100%20million%20of%20his%20own%20fortune%20despite%20having%20no%20experience%20in%20aerospace%20engineering.%20With%20its%20reusable%20rockets%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-spacex-starship-landing-super-heavy-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpaceX%3C%2Fa%3E%20overtook%20legacy%20aerospace%20giants%20to%20become%20the%20dominant%20launch%20provider%20for%20astronauts%2C%20satellites%2C%20and%20commercial%20payloads.%20Musk%20says%20his%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20space%20travel%20more%20accessible%20and%20to%20give%20life%20on%20Ear