0Twitter%20was%20part%20of%20Musk's%20'battle%20for%20the%20future%20of%20civilization'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%2C%20carrying%20a%20sink%2C%20enters%20the%20Twitter%20headquarters%20in%20San%20Francisco.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F635cefe40b271e00186b8da5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221700%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20arriving%20at%20Twitter's%20headquarters%20in%20San%20Francisco%20after%20buying%20the%20company.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20acquisition%20of%20Twitter%20in%202022%20was%20a%20big%20swing%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%2444%20billion%20one%2C%20to%20be%20exact%20%E2%80%94%20to%20address%20another%20complex%20issue%20Musk%20saw%20as%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20pandemic%20and%20civil%20rights%20unrest%2C%20Musk%20said%20he%20worried%20that%20the%20freedom%20to%20say%20anything%20you%20wanted%20was%20at%20risk.%20Buying%20Twitter%20was%20his%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20battle%20for%20the%20future%20of%20civilization%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20Twitter%20in%202022%20after%20acquiring%20it%2C%20six%20months%20before%20he%20rebranded%20it%20as%20X.%20%26quot%3BIf%20free%20speech%20is%20lost%20even%20in%20America%2C%20tyranny%20is%20all%20that%20lies%20ahead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20also%20voiced%20concerns%20about%20the%20future%20of%20artificial%20intelligence.%20He's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-isnt-backing-down-from-fight-with-open-ai-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egone%20to%20war%20with%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20that%20company's%20attention%20to%20its%20mission%2C%20which%20Musk%20helped%20craft%20as%20an%20early%20cofounder%3A%20to%20develop%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20in%20a%20way%20that%20benefits%20humanity.%20Musk%20sees%20AGI%20as%20an%20existential%20threat%2C%20and%20said%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20he%20founded%20xAI%2C%20the%20startup%20behind%20the%20Grok%20chatbot%2C%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20start%20something%20which%20I%20call%20TruthGPT%20or%20a%20maximum%20truth-seeking%20AI%20that%20tries%20to%20understand%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20universe%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20told%20Fox%20News%20in%202023%2C%20adding%20that%20xAI%20%26quot%3Bmight%20be%20the%20best%20path%20to%20safety%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bunlikely%20to%20annihilate%20humans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20also%20part%20of%20his%20stated%20reasoning%20for%20founding%20Neuralink%2C%20which%20designs%20brain%20chips%20so%20humans%20can%20interact%20with%20computers.%20The%20chip%20is%20now%20in%20trials%20and%20used%20by%20a%20handful%20of%20disabled%20patients%2C%20who%20use%20it%20to%20more%20easily%20communicate%2C%20operate%20computers%2C%20or%20play%20video%20games.%20Musk%20has%20said%20that%20the%20ability%20for%20humans%20to%20integrate%20directly%20with%20machines%20can%20help%20ensure%20human%20control%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20in%20a%202021%20podcast%20appearance%20that%20he%20created%20Neuralink%20%26quot%3Bspecifically%20to%20address%20the%20AI%20symbiosis%20problem%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20an%20existential%20threat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2234841ea0-d024-4b83-b9bb-c8aea55915c3%5C%22%3EMusk's%20political%20problem-solving%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20speaking%20at%20a%20town%20hall%20in%20Lancaster%2C%20Pennsylvania.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686b2fae3d5881a51c1cc1b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BBy%20a%20factor%20of%202%20to%201%2C%20you%20want%20a%20new%20political%20party%20and%20you%20shall%20have%20it!%26quot%3B%20Elon%20Musk%20said%20when%20ann