%3EThey%20also%20have%20a%20quarter%20of%20their%20business%20dedicated%20to%20corporate%20gifting.%20Customers%20visiting%20this%20segment%20would%20request%20gift%20items%20related%20to%20chocolate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20politely%20decline%20their%20request%20since%20chocolate%20items%20weren%E2%80%99t%20available.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20anything%20about%20chocolate%20at%20that%20time%20because%20chocolate%20was%20always%20something%20that%20we%20bought%20from%20a%20supplier%2C%E2%80%9D%20admits%20Muppala.%20However%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20branching%20out%20into%20the%20chocolate%20market%20sparked%20his%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChocolate-Making_Manam-Chocolate-Karkhana_photo-courtesy-Siddharth-Govindan_8-copy_11zon-1751876772-500x333.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChocolate-Making_Manam-Chocolate-Karkhana_photo-courtesy-Siddharth-Govindan_8-copy_11zon-1751876772-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChocolate-Making_Manam-Chocolate-Karkhana_photo-courtesy-Siddharth-Govindan_8-copy_11zon-1751876772-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChocolate-Making_Manam-Chocolate-Karkhana_photo-courtesy-Siddharth-Govindan_8-copy_11zon-1751876772-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChocolate-Making_Manam-Chocolate-Karkhana_photo-courtesy-Siddharth-Govindan_8-copy_11zon-1751876772-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChocolate-Making_Manam-Chocolate-Karkhana_photo-courtesy-Siddharth-Govindan_8-copy_11zon-1751876772-150x100.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FChocolate-Making_Manam-Chocolate-Karkhana_photo-courtesy-Siddharth-Govindan_8-copy_11zon-1751876772.jpg%201650w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-465031%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMuppala%20study%20found%20a%20key%20understanding%20that%20the%20quality%20of%20chocolate%20inherently%20depends%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20beans.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20he%20started%20mapping%20and%20contextualizing%20the%20market%20to%20understand%20what%20chocolate%20is.%20%E2%80%9CI%20quickly%20realized%20that%20anybody%20involved%20in%20the%20chocolate%20industry%20in%20India%20is%20buying%20chocolate%2C%20melting%20it%2C%20moulding%20it%2C%20adding%20nuts%2C%20flavour%2C%20and%20sea%20salt%2C%20and%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F217619%2Fdark-chocolate-health-benefits-reduced-heart-risk-improved-brain-function-buy-online-lifestyle-char01%2F%5C%22%3Epackaging%20it%20as%20their%20own%20chocolate%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20like%20enough%20sustainable%20differentiation%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Hyderabad-based%20entrepreneur%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Almond%20House%2C%20he%20understood%20that%20mithai%20is%20regional.%20Every%20region%20has%20different%20preferences.%20I%20started%20realizing%20that%20our%20younger%20people%E2%80%99s%20moods%20are%20shifting%20from%20traditional%20categories%20like%20mithai%20to%20contemporary%20modern%20and%2C%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20Western%20categories%20like%20patisserie%20chocolates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20every%20city%20has%20two%20or%20three%20chocolate%20brands%20like%20his%20mithai%20brands%2C%20but%20if%20they%20all%20source%20the%20same%20ingredients%20from%20the%20same%20multinational%20supplier%2C%20the%20end%20product%20will%20be%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELiving%20with%20Farmers%2C%20Learning%20from%20the%20Soil%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20researching%20the%20art%20of%20chocolate%20making%2C%20small-batch%20chocolate%20production%2C%20and%20the%20principles%20of%20craft%20chocolate%2C%20his%20study%20found%20a%20key%20understanding%20that%20the%20quality%20of%20chocolate%20inherently%20depends%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20beans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20prompted%20him%20to%20search%20further%20about%20the%20origin%20of%20beans%2C%20and%20that%20led%20him%20to%20farms%20in%202018%2C%20where%20he%20spent%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20with%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20West%20Godavari%20district%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20the%20farmers%20were%20skeptical.%20They%20viewed%20me%20as%20an%20outsider%20from%20the%20city%20doing%20something%20new.%20I%20lived%20among%20them%20to%20win%20their%20trust.%20It%20took%20two%20to%20three%20years%20to%20build%20their%20confidence%20in%20me.%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20business%20with%20them%20and%20help%20them%20make%20more%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20businessperson%20continues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms-of-Member-Farmers_West-Godavari_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_2550e_11zon-1751876747-500x750.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms-of-Member-Farmers_West-Godavari_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_2550e_11zon-1751876747-500x750.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCacao-Farms-of-Member-Farmers_West-Godavari_Photo-Hashim-