much%20impact%20the%20soil%2C%20the%20climate%2C%20or%20our%20handling%20could%20have%20on%20the%20flavour%20of%20the%20cocoa%20beans.%20The%20engagement%20has%20enhanced%20our%20understanding%20that%20cocoa%20carries%20the%20taste%20of%20the%20land%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20our%20job%20to%20bring%20that%20out%20with%20our%20efforts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20different%20about%20working%20with%20them%20is%20the%20respect%20they%20have%20for%20our%20offering.%20They%20pay%20us%20above-market%20rates%20for%20our%20fruit%2C%20but%20more%20than%20that%2C%20we%20see%20the%20value%20of%20what%20we%20grow.%20When%20our%20cacao%20goes%20through%20their%20Fermentery%20with%20all%20the%20scientific%20fermentation%20and%20drying%20processes%20that%20they%20carry%20out%20and%20it%20is%20turned%20into%20fine%20flavour%20cacao%20beans%2C%20it%20gives%20us%20tremendous%20pride.%20We%20know%20exactly%20where%20our%20fruit%20is%20going%2C%20and%20we%20know%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20made%20into%20something%20truly%20special.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20farmers%20here%20produced%20cocoa%20in%20a%20conventional%20method%2C%20Muppala%20faced%20another%20challenge%20related%20to%20the%20genetics%20of%20cocoa%20in%20India%2C%20which%20is%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20the%20history%20of%20its%20arrival%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-500x739.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chocolate%20crafted%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F3_Cacao-Pod_West-Godavari-District-AP_Photo-Hashim-Badani_DSC_3260-copy-2_11zon-1751876730-500x739.jpg%2050