e%20travel%20less%20than%20500%20km%20before%20being%20converted%20into%20chocolate.%20This%20is%20in%20comparison%20to%20most%20other%20chocolate%20(especially%20Industrial%20chocolate)%20which%20first%20travels%20as%20a%20bean%20and%20then%20as%20finished%20chocolate%20on%20average%2012%2C000%20to%2015%2C000%20kms%20on%20cargo%20sea%20routes%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chef%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAll%20about%20the%20man%20behind%20the%20brand%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20but%20most%20of%20his%20childhood%20was%20spent%20away.%20He%20grew%20up%20in%20Sahyadri%20School%20KFI%2C%20Pune%20(Jiddu%20Krishnamurti%20Boarding%20School).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20alternative%20schools.%20We%20grew%20up%20on%20a%20hill%2C%20climbing%20rocks%20and%20trees.%20Every%20day%2C%20the%20whole%20school%20would%20assemble%20at%20six%20in%20the%20evening%20to%20watch%20the%20sunset.%20There%20were%20only%20200%20of%20us%20on%20that%20hill%2C%20including%20teachers%20and%20service%20staff.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20exams%20till%20Class%209%2C%E2%80%9D%20Muppala%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2015%2C%20he%20took%20a%20year%20off%20to%20go%20on%20a%20solo%20trip%20by%20train%20after%20completing%20his%20Class%2010%20in%202008.%20Then%20he%20went%20to%20Canada%2C%20lived%20in%20Vancouver%20for%20about%20seven%20years%20to%20complete%20his%20education%2C%20and%20returned%20to%20India%20in%202013.%20Muppala%20has%20a%20sister%20who%20lives%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDExHnlyv0Ez%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDExHnlyv0Ez%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2F