been%20the%20Himalayan%20Homestay%20Programme%2C%20launched%20in%202001.%20It%20began%20with%20a%20simple%20idea%2C%20instead%20of%20building%20tourist%20camps%20that%20generate%20waste%2C%20why%20not%20have%20visitors%20stay%20in%20local%20homes%3F%20The%20conservancy%20surveyed%20villages%20and%20found%20strong%20support%20for%20the%20concept.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154904.366_11zon-1751624387.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20the%20centre%20of%20Ladakh's%20conservation%20effort%20is%20the%20Snow%20Leopard%20Conservancy%20India%20Trust%20(SLC-IT)%2C%20an%20initiative%20founded%20in%202003%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Indiaspend%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154904.366_11zon-1751624387.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154904.366_11zon-1751624387-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154904.366_11zon-1751624387-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154904.366_11zon-1751624387-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154904.366_11zon-1751624387-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-462660%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20centre%20of%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20conservation%20effort%20is%20the%20Snow%20Leopard%20Conservancy%20India%20Trust%20(SLC-IT)%2C%20an%20initiative%20founded%20in%202003%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Indiaspend%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20more%20than%20200%20homestays%20operate%20in%2040%20Ladakhi%20villages.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20funds%20are%20created%20uniquely%3A%2010%20percent%20of%20all%20homestays%E2%80%99%20income%20goes%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98village%20conservation%20fund%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20used%20by%20villagers%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F276049%2Fkerala-man-transforms-dumpyard-into-beautiful-garden%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etree%20planting%2C%20garbage%20cleaning%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20maintenance%20of%20their%20cultural%20heritage%2C%20such%20as%20mani%20walls%2C%20%3Cem%3Echortens%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20sacred%20juniper%20stands%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dr%20Namgail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoosing%20to%20stay%20in%20one%20of%20these%20homestays%20generates%20funds%20for%20communities%20that%20they%20use%20to%20protect%20their%20mountain%20environment.%20The%20villagers%20also%20host%20guests%20on%20a%20rotational%20basis.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20done%20so%20that%20no%20single%20family%20can%20monopolise%20the%20tourists.%20Because%20if%20that%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20it%20would%20create%20disharmony%20in%20the%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESafeguarding%20livestock%20and%20landscapes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Conservancy%20also%20supports%20the%20construction%20of%20predator-proof%20livestock%20enclosures%20using%20low-cost%20and%20locally%20sourced%20materials.%20%E2%80%9CVillagers%20provide%20the%20labour%20while%20SLC-IT%20provides%20wire%20mesh%2C%20doorframes%2C%20beams%2C%20and%20wooden%20poles%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Namgail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20snow%20leopard%20plays%20